social_posts.post_text: Sports x Innovation 🔋💪🏽🔥 Had a great time at the LA Sports Innovation conference! Thanks for having me. 🙏🏽

Doing great things… with great people 💪🏽 

2023 here we come 🔥 #LandspireGroup

As the restraints of the pandemic eased up and people started getting together again in 2022, I spent a lot of time aligning myself and Landspire Group with others who have similar missions in Real Estate and Impact. 
Thanks so much to Revitate for the work you all do, and for honoring me at your 2022 Social Impact summit. 

Excited to continue the mission in 2023! 
🙏🏽🙏🏽🙏🏽 

“Entrepreneurial leaders are increasingly finding unique and innovative pathways to build great businesses with even greater social impact.

Revitate recently honored four such “Social Impact Champions” at our annual Social Impact Summit:

 -  Julie Uhrman, Angel City Football Club. 
 -  Josh Childress, Landspire Group 
 -  Trevor Pryce, Outlook Company
 -  Heidi Zuckerman, OCMA / Orange County Museum of Art

Josh’s company, LandSpire, believes that the greatest financial returns come from strategic investments that transform communities and the lives of those living in them. Josh explains that LandSpire was founded with the purpose of redeveloping underserved communities of color that were once defined by small businesses, livable-wage jobs, and a thriving middle class. The company provides these communities with the resources needed to thrive and addresses prevalent various socio-economic challenges, while also generating strong returns for investors.”
Landspire Group 2023 🔥🔥🔥 #Investor #Owner #RealEstateDevelopment #2023
